ActCanadian Dairy Commission Act
SubjectAgreement on Eastern Milk Pooling Re: coordinated marketing of dairy products
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN DAIRY COMMISSION to enter into the AGREEMENT ON THE EASTERN CANADIAN MILK POOLING with the provinces or with provincial milk marketing boards or agencies in Prince Edward Island, Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, Quebec and Ontario, for the purpose of coordinating the marketing of dairy products.
